date: 2024-12-30 12:00:00 -0000
author: Gunnar Ekelöf
quote: "A gentle rain falls,"
subject: Scandinavian Nature Poetry (Late 19th century)
permalink: /Scandinavian Nature Poetry (Late 19th century)/Gunnar Ekelöf/Gunnar Ekelöf - Rains Lullaby
---

A gentle rain falls,
  kissing the earth awake,
  nurturing roots hidden deep,
  coaxing life from the soil.
  The sound is a lullaby,
  a soothing balm
  for restless hearts,
  as the world drinks greedily,
  ready to burst into bloom once more.

- Gunnar Ekelöf
